Should I speak to you in sign language?

678
01:07:07,763 --> 01:07:09,697
Paul, I can't believe
what she's saying.

679
01:07:12,768 --> 01:07:15,202
Oh My God...
Michelle!

680
01:07:16,638 --> 01:07:20,005
Michelle!
- No, Mrs. McNally. Leave her alone.

681
01:07:21,844 --> 01:07:24,608
With every fall, she'll rise higher.

682
01:07:25,647 --> 01:07:28,616
I fell.

683
01:07:29,518 --> 01:07:30,576
That's the spirit.

684
01:07:32,988 --> 01:07:40,019
I want you to walk alone,
without any help.

685
01:07:41,530 --> 01:07:46,297
then right. Understood?

686
01:08:01,483 --> 01:08:03,815
JoJo... go slow... l'm getting old.

687
01:08:05,187 --> 01:08:06,654
Oh! I'm so sorry.

688
01:08:20,702 --> 01:08:21,327
Where is she going?

689
01:08:25,541 --> 01:08:26,940
Where... are you going?

690
01:08:28,043 --> 01:08:31,570
No no no... This is the
wrong way... it's this way.

691
01:08:32,081 --> 01:08:34,515
No... it's... tch!
We're getting late...

692
01:08:34,716 --> 01:08:41,349
Come on... yes, hurry up

693
01:08:44,059 --> 01:08:44,855
Yes, come on...

694
01:08:47,963 --> 01:08:50,022
Run, run, run!
Yes!

695
01:08:55,237 --> 01:08:56,704
Come on, come on... hurry up.

696
01:08:58,073 --> 01:08:59,097
- Present.

697
01:08:59,908 --> 01:09:01,705
- Present

698
01:09:02,010 --> 01:09:03,705
- Present

699
01:09:04,880 --> 01:09:05,869

700
01:09:09,885 --> 01:09:12,718
- Present.

