01:09:14,089 --> 01:09:17,752
"There was so much to learn
and there was such little time."

702
01:09:18,594 --> 01:09:19,720
"24 hours without tiring..."

703
01:09:20,562 --> 01:09:25,226
"Your fingers would speak to me."

704
01:09:25,801 --> 01:09:29,134
Whether life starts from
the womb or from the earth...

705
01:09:30,105 --> 01:09:36,066
its journey starts from darkness
and ends in darkness.

706
01:09:37,513 --> 01:09:40,971
One day we will all have to pass
through this darkness...

707
01:09:41,450 --> 01:09:48,014
and reach into the light.

708
01:09:48,423 --> 01:09:51,722
"One day, we all have to go through
the darkness, to... light..."

709
01:09:52,494 --> 01:09:54,758
"New doors opened up for me..."

710
01:09:55,497 --> 01:09:59,991
"new friends, new stories,
new poetry..."

711
01:10:01,170 --> 01:10:02,933
"a new way of looking at the world"

712
01:10:03,705 --> 01:10:06,503
"what you see is what you dream'

713
01:10:08,377 --> 01:10:11,540
No. She, she... she disagrees
with the poet

714
01:10:12,714 --> 01:10:16,343
Eyes don't see dreams
but the mind does.

715
01:10:17,152 --> 01:10:22,886
I can't see with my eyes,
yet I dream.

716
01:10:23,458 --> 01:10:28,122
Our dream is that one-day
I would graduate.

717
01:10:40,175 --> 01:10:43,872
Are you ready?

718
01:10:44,079 --> 01:10:45,137
Ready...

719
01:10:46,682 --> 01:10:48,980
Tree...
- Tree...

720
01:10:49,918 --> 01:10:52,250
Burr...
- Butterfly...

721
01:10:52,854 --> 01:10:54,981
Bir...
- Bird...

722
01:10:55,524 --> 01:10:57,321
Fish...
- Fish...

723
01:10:58,527 --> 01:11:00,154
Bee...
- Bee...

724
01:11:08,337 --> 01:11:13,001
"The best years of my life..."

725
01:11:13,909 --> 01:11:16,036
"memories of which
bring joy even today"

726
01:11:30,592 --> 01:11:32,025
It's ok...

727
01:11:33,428 --> 01:11:34,360
It's all right!

728
01:11:41,703 --> 01:11:43,364
What? Tickly?

729
01:11:54,716 --> 01:11:58,709
It's not going to snow.
Please concentrate on your studies

730
01:12:00,088 --> 01:12:03,717
No, no... you wont need the
umbrella at all, concentrate.

731
01:12:17,806 --> 01:12:19,899
Give me the umbrella.
Hey stop it...

732
01:12:20,108 --> 01:12:21,075
Give me the umbrella...

733
01:12:21,276 --> 01:12:22,243
Give me the umbrella...
give... me... The umbrella

